t: Amazon.com: Profound Mysteries III: CDs & Vinyl
s: Profound Mysteries III from Royksopp is easily the best in the series. Only 10 tracks but each track is lengthy. The tracks are superb, building rhythms and melodies throughout. The tracks with vocals are sublime. Absolutely brilliant and highly recommended.
